#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:2
msgid "Pending removal in Python 3.21"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:4
msgid ":mod:`abc`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:6
msgid ""
"Soft-deprecated since Python 3.3 :class:`abc.abstractclassmethod`, :class:"
"`abc.abstractstaticmethod`, and :class:`abc.abstractproperty` now raise a :"
"exc:`DeprecationWarning`. These classes will be removed in Python 3.21, "
"instead use :func:`abc.abstractmethod` with :func:`classmethod`, :func:"
"`staticmethod`, and :class:`property` respectively."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:13
msgid ":mod:`ast`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:15
msgid ""
"Classes ``slice``, ``Index``, ``ExtSlice``, ``Suite``, ``Param``, "
"``AugLoad`` and ``AugStore``, will be removed in Python 3.21. These types "
"are not generated by the parser or accepted by the code generator."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../deprecations/pending-removal-in-3.21.rst:18
msgid ""
"The ``dims`` property of ``ast.Tuple`` will be removed in Python 3.21. Use "
"the ``ast.Tuple.elts`` property instead."
msgstr ""
